s Theme for WordPress</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/better-wp-security/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>iThemes Security (formerly Better WP Security)</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=better-wp-security&amp;_wpnonce=0bbcf85d9f&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''iThemes Security (formerly Better WP Security)''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
