(537, '_transient_mgm_current_messages', '<b>MGM V.1.8.45 Changelog</b><br>\r\n<b>09/08/2014</b><br>\r\n<font color=\\"red\\">-fixed- Wordpress 4.0 registration issues which includes validating the fields</font>. Please provide any feedback<br>\r\n-fixed- The account status problem if multiple purchase is enabled and the same pack is selected for move subscription pack setting<br>\r\n-fixed- Custom purchase URL for purchase another membership level<br>\r\n-fixed- Pagination issue for the Coupon page<br>\r\n-fixed- Partial refunds in PayPal won\\''t deactivate the account<br>\r\n-added- Tag protection<br>\r\n-added- German terms translation support<br>\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>\r\n<b>MGM V.1.8.44 Changelog</b><br>\r\n<b>08/14/2014</b><br>\r\n-added- redirect_to parameter will now override global login redirect settings<br>\r\n-added- Mailchimp lists will auto-populate in admin side for Membership Mappings<br>\r\n-added- Infusionsoft Tag/Group Id are auto populated in admin side for Membership Mappings<br>\r\n-added- GetResponse AR Campaigns will auto-populate in admin side for Membership Mappings<br>\r\n-added- Constant Contact lists will auto-populate in admin side for Membership Mappings<br>\r\n-added- Awever lists will auto-populate in admin side for Membership Mappings<br>\r\n-added- Support to unsubscribe from email lists if user unsubscribes from the site (Aweber,MailChimp, InfusionSoft, ConstantContact and GetResponse)<br>\r\n-added- Membership level based shortcode in expiration reminder email to show different content. Ex: [user_account_is#gold]email content[/user_account_is]<br>\r\n-added- Terms and Conditions date in user export<br>\r\n-added- Timeout setting in eway module with default timeout 30 seconds<br>\r\n-added- Missing translation strings<br>\r\n-added- Support for PHP 5.4<br>\r\n-added- (Beta) Credit Card update feature for PayPal Pro and Authorize.Net<br>\r\n-added- CSS classes for Register & Purchase, Purchase Only, Login & Purchase links<br>\r\n-added- Coupon support for Stripe gateway<br>\r\n-added- Show/Hide Unsubscribe Option<br>\r\n-added- Registration IP address<br>\r\n-fixed- Captcha text issue when there\\''s only one word is displaying<br>\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>\r\n<b>MGM V.1.8.43 Changelog</b><br>\r\n<b>06/24/2014</b><br>\r\n-added- Infusionsoft autoresponder<br>\r\n-added- Individual subscription pack save option in admin<br>\r\n-added- Receipt Email for Stripe PayPerPost payment<br>\r\n-added- Compatibility with Limit Login Attempt plugin<br>\r\n-added- Remote post connection error notification emails to administrator setting<br>\r\n-added- [[name]] short code support for widgets<br>\r\n-added- Date shortcode support for emails<br>\r\n-fixed- Email field is empty error message when user logins in some cases<br>\r\n-fixed- Translation issue with the word Active<br>\r\n-fixed- Conflict with Ultimate CSV Importer PRO plugin<br>\r\n-fixed- Payment denied issue when Purchase Another Membership Level form is used with PayPal<br>\r\n-fixed- Mexican currency. Now it\\''s set as MXN and not MXR<br>\r\n-fixed- Same \\''Sort Order\\'' number for subscription packs causing different display output<br>\r\n-fixed- The registration issue if an autoresponder module is enabled, but autoresponder field is not enabled<br>\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>', 'no'),
