(320, '_transient_mgm_current_messages', '<b>MGM V.1.8.43 Changelog</b><br>\r\n<b>06/24/2014</b><br>\r\n-added- Infusionsoft autoresponder<br>\r\n-added- Individual subscription pack save option in admin<br>\r\n-added- Receipt Email for Stripe PayPerPost payment<br>\r\n-added- Compatibility with Limit Login Attempt plugin<br>\r\n-added- Remote post connection error notification emails to administrator setting<br>\r\n-added- [[name]] short code support for widgets<br>\r\n-added- Date shortcode support for emails<br>\r\n-fixed- Email field is empty error message when user logins in some cases<br>\r\n-fixed- Translation issue with the word Active<br>\r\n-fixed- Conflict with Ultimate CSV Importer PRO plugin<br>\r\n-fixed- Payment denied issue when Purchase Another Membership Level form is used with PayPal<br>\r\n-fixed- Mexican currency. Now it\\''s set as MXN and not MXR<br>\r\n-fixed- Same \\''Sort Order\\'' number for subscription packs causing different display output<br>\r\n-fixed- The registration issue if an autoresponder module is enabled, but autoresponder field is not enabled<br>\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>\r\n<b>MGM V.1.8.42 Changelog</b><br>\r\n<b>05/09/2014</b><br>\r\n-added- Constant Contact list Ids are auto populated in admin side<br>\r\n-added- Disable log folder option<br>\r\n-added- Long date format support to [user_purchased_contents] shortcode<br>\r\n-added- Onetime payment support for Stripe gateway<br>\r\n-added- Auto scroll-up when credit card details have an error<br>\r\n-added- Hyperlink support to the url field in public profile and member list pages<br>\r\n-added- Default Wordpress password reset to the front side of the site<br>\r\n-fixed- In profile search page modified labels are not showing properly<br>\r\n-fixed- Multiple currency issue on extend form<br>\r\n-fixed- PayPerPost search option<br>\r\n-fixed- Subscription pack setting save issue for large user base<br>\r\n-fixed- Authorize.net related expiration issues. New response messages added<br>\r\n-fixed- New Stripe API changes applied<br>\r\n-fixed- Coupons and Addon menus were scrolling down at the bottom<br>\r\n-fixed- Confirm email option is not disabled<br>\r\n-fixed- Broken translation strings<br>\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>', 'no'),
